Plans for 0.5.0
===============

  * General
      - Use "." as decimal for time
      - Put a .pot file in the trunk?
      - Mime-type registration?
      - count vs. amount
      - Profile!

  * gtk
      - Framerate conversion available for time-based subs
      - No need to check if translator-credits is translated
      - UIM name: /ui/menubar/edit/edit
      - Spell-check dialog mnemonics: Join _Back, Join _Forward
      - Targets! The fucking targets!
      - Menu item locations: Framerate, Select Video, Headers
      - Remove Unselect All menu item?
      - Output window not Ctrl+Alt+O?
      - Debug dialog should not crash if no enchant

  * setup.py / setup.cfg
      - Don't install any testing
      - python 2.5 uninstall?
      - Remove setup.cfg?
      - setup.py: destination vs. configure (Arch)
          - setup.py install --prefix=/usr --root=tmp/pkg
          - Add a destdir option to install
          - finalize_options: x = os.path.join(destdir, x)
          - paths.py: if destdir: ...
      - Use intltool-merge for gaupol.desktop file translations?
          - See alacarte source code
      - clean command
      - Do setup.py install options work?
          --prefix           OK
          --exec-prefix
          --home
          --install-base
          --install-platbase
          --root
          --install-purelib
          --install-lib
          --install-scripts
          --install-data

  New Features:
    [W] Find and replace
    [?] Encoding autodetection: http://chardet.feedparser.org/

  Improvements:
    [D] New icon
    [D] Applied GNOME Goal 2.1: Install theme-friendly icons
    [D] Support default browsers on KDE and Mac OSX as well
    [D] Better video player defaults on Windows
    [D] Developer-specific options to gaupol made into separate scripts
    [W] Testing framework made compatible with py.test

  Bug Fixes:
    [ ] Video selection dialog's file filter should default to video
    [ ] Gaupol hangs if video player not closed before exit
    [ ] Spell-check suggestion list does not scroll to top with new word
    [D] Icon field in the desktop file should not include extension

  Dependencies:
    [W] Psyco no longer used

  New Translations:
    * Polish (po)

